Danny Nucci https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danny_Nucci 0 Daniel Antonelli Nucci (born September 15, 1968) is an American actor known for supporting roles in blockbuster films including The Rock, Crimson Tide, and Titanic and his lead role as Mike Foster in The Fosters.
